Design doc for VJTEYE App
//

//
Classes:
1) Department - Sites, Department-name, Department-id, addSite(),getters, setters, static count. 
2) Sites - Site-name, Site-id, Site unique-id = Department-id + Site-id, Site-description, static count.
3) Note(Nice to have/Useless) - note-date, note-content
4) SiteDetector - gets site-id from web server
UI design:
Two Layouts-
1st layout will have Camera
2nd layout will have Recycler View
3rd layout is invisible and becomes visible on clicking description

